        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crumble your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into the pan and add your<strong> curry powder</strong> and<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
