    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>warmed rice</strong> to the pan with the <strong>tomato stock </strong>and increase the heat to high</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 2 min or until the mushrooms have softened – this is your <strong>plant-based mushroom biryani</strong></p>",
