    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your<strong> cucumber</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated cucumber</strong> with your <strong>coconut</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and a pinch of<strong> pepper </strong>in a bowl – this is your<strong> coconut cucumber raita</strong></p>",
