      "instruction": "<p>Dollop the <strong>plant-based mushroom</strong> <strong>biryani </strong>over the <strong>coconut cucumber raita</strong>, garnish with the <strong>crispy onions</strong> and dig in</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
